# integer-invalid-radix-digits

## Input

```
a 0b2
b 0o8
c 0xG

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..18
  ENTRY@0..6
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "a"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    INTEGER@2..5
      NUMERAL@2..5 "0b2"
    NEWLINE@5..6 "\n"
  ENTRY@6..12
    WORD_KEY@6..7
      WORD@6..7 "b"
    SPACE@7..8 " "
    INTEGER@8..11
      NUMERAL@8..11 "0o8"
    NEWLINE@11..12 "\n"
  ENTRY@12..18
    WORD_KEY@12..13
      WORD@12..13 "c"
    SPACE@13..14 " "
    LINE_STRING@14..17
      STRING@14..17 "0xG"
    NEWLINE@17..18 "\n"
```

